The,Yahoo,Image,Search,API,is,part,of,BOSS,Build,your,Own,Search,Service,which,provides,API,access,to,Yahoo,s,web,news,and,image,search,technology,Unlike,other,search,APIs,developers,can,use,BOSS,technology,with,very,few,restrictions,The,Image,Search,API,provides,access,to,Yahoo,s,image,search,technology,and,allows,users,to,search,the,Internet,for,images,It,uses,a,RESTful,protocol,and,responses,are,formatted,in,either,XML,JSON,or,PHP